{"id":151235,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/rms两本著作发布2-0版/","date":"2011-05-10T03:00:45Z","modified":"2011-05-10T03:00:45Z","title":"RMS两本著作发布2.0版","content":"<p>自由软件基金会（FSF）宣布，其创始人兼主席Richard Stallman的两本著作发布了2.0版。其一是文集选《Free Software, Free Society》(PDF)，其二是半自传《Free as in Freedom: Richard Stallman and the Free Software Revolution》（PDF）。鉴于反DRM的立场，两本书的电子版将只提供PDF版，不会在Amazon Kindle或其它私有电子书平台上发布。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14af1d19/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=RMS%E4%B8%A4%E6%9C%AC%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%832.0%E7%89%88&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F09%2F029232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=RMS%E4%B8%A4%E6%9C%AC%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%832.0%E7%89%88&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F09%2F029232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091707226/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14af1d19/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091707226/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14af1d19/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=wHFT7yPmTdY:_7PaHEG8vuY:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=wHFT7yPmTdY:_7PaHEG8vuY:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"htt